:"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"This utility helps to define wether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"See for example ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio"}}}